        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（计全上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "计全 （缕缕金） 闻凶信，心内忙，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "两脚不消停，祸起萧墙。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "此事如何了，心中愁伤。"
        },
        {
          "character": "计全",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺，计全。适才在城中闲游，街市上纷纷言讲：都说京城之内，奉旨擒拿黄三"
        },
        {
          "character": "计全",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "泰。此事有些不好，也不知起因何事。我不免报与三叔知道，也好作个准备。"
        },
        {
          "character": "计全",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "急忙前去怎停当，"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [],
      "stats": {
        "line_counts": {
          "stage_direction": 4
        },
        "singing_ratio": 0.0,
        "dominant_style_family": null,
        "musical_styles": []
      },
      "scene_feature": [
        0.0,
        0.3333,
        0.6667,
        0.0,
        0.0,
        1,
        0.0,
        0.0
      ]
    },
    {
      "scene_index": 2,
      "label": "第二场",
      "characters_present": [
        "计全",
        "黄三泰",
        "黄用"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（黄三泰上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄三泰",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "舍命威名谁不服，方显男儿大丈夫。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄三泰",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺，黄三泰。只因洪海内闯了围，打死一只斑斓猛虎，那勇力王爱我是条好汉，"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄三泰",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不但不加罪与我，反赏我黄挂一件，放我回家。将黄挂供奉先堂。想我黄三"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄三泰",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "泰，身在绿林，也算得名魁第一。到今日静掩柴扉，好不快乐也。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄三泰",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "心安静乐守家乡，"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄三泰",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "弃绿林倒也欢畅。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄三泰",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "喜得他心敏性刚。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖内乌鸦叫〗。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄三泰",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呀呔！"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄三泰",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "乌鸦声声喊叫，"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄三泰",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "此事儿令人难详。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（计全上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "计全",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "忙将京中事，报与三叔知。"
        },
        {
          "character": "计全",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "三叔在上，侄儿拜揖。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄三泰",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "计贤侄，你从哪里来？"
        },
        {
          "character": "计全",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我从城中而来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄三泰",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "既从城中而来，如何这等慌张？"
        },
        {
          "character": "计全",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "三叔，不好了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄三泰",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怎么样？慢慢说来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "计全",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "三叔，我耳闻京中现今奉旨捉拿三叔，不知所因何故，前来送信呵！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（水底鱼） 纷纷言讲：擒拿黄三泰，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "速速准备，早早安排安排。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄三泰",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "到底为着何事？"
        },
        {
          "character": "计全",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "并不晓得所为何事。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄三泰",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这等好生奇怪也！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（紫花序） 听此言心中暗想，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "莫非是洪海那事一桩？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "料也无妨。"
        },
        {
          "character": "计全",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "三叔说哪里话来，我想此事既言奉旨，事来的不轻。万一官人前来，一定被他"
        },
        {
          "character": "计全",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "们擒获。这一押送进京，岂不将三叔一世英名付与流水？"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄三泰",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "依你便怎么样？"
        },
        {
          "character": "计全",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "若依小侄，三叔可知两句俗言，三十六着，走为上策，躲避躲避，方为妙处。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄三泰",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "满口胡言！你可知你三叔一世为人，岂不知大丈夫舍一命轻似牛毛，立美名传"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄三泰",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "与后世也！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（紫花序） 俺本是堂堂猛烈大丈夫，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "便一死待何妨？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哪怕他乱箭刀伤。"
        },
        {
          "character": "计全",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "三叔，小侄到有一计在此。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄三泰",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有何计？"
        },
        {
          "character": "计全",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "曾记得那年，你我叔侄从张家口而来，路遇白马李七侯一事。那时彭公卸任，"
        },
        {
          "character": "计全",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "多亏三叔用金镖各省借银，才把彭公复任。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄三泰",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "过往之事。提他何用？"
        },
        {
          "character": "计全",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "三叔，这如今彭公官升通州，你老人家何不自投到通州彭公案下，一来方知京"
        },
        {
          "character": "计全",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "中所为何事，二则也显三叔的英名也！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（鬼三台） 想京中捉拿人非等闲，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "劝三叔早早把程途趱。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "黄三泰 （鬼三台） 听他言巧舌话辩，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺如今投奔便见奇冤。"
        },
        {
          "character": "计全",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "计全言之有理。俺如今急奔通州去，会李七侯贤弟，可要你随我前去，或吉或"
        },
        {
          "character": "计全",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "凶，往还也得个信息。"
        },
        {
          "character": "计全",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小侄理当随去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄三泰",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "快些备马。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（计全应，下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄三泰",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "黄用哪里？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（黄用上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄用",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有何吩咐？"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄三泰",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我如今同计全要上通州有紧急事。家中一切好生照管，如有人来寻我，只言我"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄三泰",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "上了通州了。听我吩咐！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（鬼三台） 俺如今访故友，要把程途趱，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "在家中劳你照管。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（黄用下。计全上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "计全",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将马备好。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄三泰",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将马带过来。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（计全带马。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄三泰",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "计全紧紧加鞭，随我快些趱路。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（天净沙） 跨雕鞍，趱程途，离家乡，大丈夫焉肯留恋，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺如今不想回还。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "沿途上，百草香，无心观览。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（黄三泰、计全同下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
        {
          "edge": "黄三泰→计全",
          "turns": 11
