    {
      "scene_index": 3,
      "label": "第三场",
      "characters_present": [
        "刘胜",
        "贾信",
        "郭保",
        "马明",
        "黑熊"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（黑熊、贾信、马明、郭保、刘胜同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "刘胜 （同吹腔） 闻凶信事由关心，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "寻找七侯到衙门。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黑熊",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "黑熊。"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾信",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "贾信。"
        },
        {
          "character": "马明",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "马明。"
        },
        {
          "character": "郭保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "郭保。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘胜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "刘胜。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黑熊",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "列位请了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾信、马明、郭保、刘胜",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黑熊",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "前者到京探望飞天豹武七哥，是他对我言道：有部文去到绍兴去拿黄三哥，是"
        },
        {
          "character": "黑熊",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我追问所因何事擒拿。"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾信",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是了。何必追问，想是因为洪海闯了围场的那件事。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黑熊",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众位，武七哥言过：这件事须得通知白马李七哥知道，大家共同商议，若是疏"
        },
        {
          "character": "黑熊",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "虞，大家齐到绍兴，做个准备。"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾信、马明、郭保、刘胜",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "言之有理，大家前去。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（同吹腔） 肝胆朋友情义深，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "方显江湖在绿林。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同下。）"
