    {
      "scene_index": 4,
      "label": "第四场",
      "characters_present": [
        "刘胜",
        "李七侯",
        "贾信",
        "郭保",
        "马明",
        "黑熊"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（李七侯上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "李七侯",
          "line_type": "引子",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "义气过天表，俺胸中，常怀结交。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李七侯",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "倾心保贤宰，州衙辨忠良。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李七侯",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺，李七侯。自从那日在山东帮助黄三哥，在李家店治服窦尔墩，散后已七、"
        },
        {
          "character": "李七侯",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "八载不曾相遇。时常挂念，意欲前去探望，怎奈官衙之事缠绕在身，不能前去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李七侯",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "正是："
        },
        {
          "character": "李七侯",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "肝胆相照结义友，空自思念在心头。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（黑熊、贾信、马明、郭保、刘胜同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "刘胜 （同吹腔） 方才衙内去问信，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "言说他在议事厅。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李七侯",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "李七哥。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李七侯",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众家弟兄请坐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黑熊、贾信、马明、郭保、刘胜",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有坐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李七侯",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众位从哪里来？"
        },
        {
          "character": "黑熊",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "七哥，前者我到京城探望武七哥。他对我说：有部文去到绍兴，擒拿黄三哥，"
        },
        {
          "character": "黑熊",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不知所因何故呵？"
        },
        {
          "character": "黑熊",
          "line_type": "吹腔",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "听说此事吃一惊，"
        },
        {
          "character": "黑熊",
          "line_type": "吹腔",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "特地前来报七兄。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李七侯",
          "line_type": "吹腔",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老来三哥遇此事，"
        },
        {
          "character": "李七侯",
          "line_type": "吹腔",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "令人心下气难平。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李七侯",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "原来如此。你等在此略等片时，待我到衙中打听消息，内中有常上京走差之人，"
        },
        {
          "character": "李七侯",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一问便知明白。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黑熊、贾信、马明、郭保、刘胜",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "七哥早去早来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李七侯",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "何劳嘱咐，俺就去也。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李七侯",
          "line_type": "吹腔",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "离了官厅衙中去，"
        },
        {
          "character": "李七侯",
          "line_type": "吹腔",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "急忙打听事一宗。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（李七侯下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "刘胜 （同吹腔） 但见七哥扬长去，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "专等回来听信音。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
