      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（黄三泰、计全同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄三泰",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "偕叔侄在途路跋山涉水，"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄三泰",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "离城池却不远就在眼前。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄三泰",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "计全，一到通州，你将我的坐骥带去，寻找李七叔，我在衙门内等你。"
        },
        {
          "character": "计全",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小侄遵命。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（计全下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄三泰",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你看计全此去，俺不免急报官衙便了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄三泰",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "抖精神甩虎步直奔衙内，"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄三泰",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "舍性命到官衙去见彭公。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（黄三泰下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
        {
          "edge": "黄三泰→计全",
          "turns": 1
