    {
      "scene_index": 6,
      "label": "第六场",
      "characters_present": [
        "刘胜",
        "计全",
        "贾信",
        "郭保",
        "马明",
        "黑熊"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（计全上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "计全",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "奉叔命到前面寻找白马，"
        },
        {
          "character": "计全",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "猛抬头看见了吏事官厅。"
        },
        {
          "character": "计全",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来此已是，待我问来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "计全",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "里面有人么？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（黑熊上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "黑熊",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "闷闷官厅坐，不见有回音。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黑熊",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀，原来是计兄到了吓，这匹坐骥是黄三爷的，三爷哪里去了？"
        },
        {
          "character": "计全",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "说来话长。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黑熊",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这等，将马带进来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黑熊",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众家弟兄快来！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（贾信、马明、郭保、刘胜同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "黑熊",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "计兄到了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾信、马明、郭保、刘胜",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "计兄在哪里？"
        },
        {
          "character": "计全",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众位请了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "黑熊、贾信、马明、郭保、刘胜",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请问计兄，你一人二骥，黄三哥现在那里？"
        },
        {
          "character": "计全",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众位有所不知：只因京中的部文去到绍兴，要拿我三叔，也不知所为何来？那"
        },
        {
          "character": "计全",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "时我三叔就要自投官衙。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黑熊、贾信、马明、郭保、刘胜",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "果然是一条好汉。后来便怎样？"
        },
        {
          "character": "计全",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是我言道三叔呵！"
        },
        {
          "character": "计全",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我叔侄离家乡来到此地，"
        },
        {
          "character": "计全",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "见彭公与七叔早早安排。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黑熊、贾信、马明、郭保、刘胜",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这如今黄三哥到底往哪里去了？"
        },
        {
          "character": "计全",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "三叔将马交付与我前来，寻找李七叔，他如今直奔州衙去了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黑熊、贾信、马明、郭保、刘胜",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怎么讲？三哥直奔衙中去了？此话是真？"
        },
        {
          "character": "计全",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是真。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黑熊、贾信、马明、郭保、刘胜",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "果然。"
        },
        {
          "character": "计全",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "果然。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黑熊、贾信、马明、郭保、刘胜",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好汉子吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "黑熊、贾信、马明、郭保、刘胜",
          "line_type": "同唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "黄三哥真乃是英雄好汉，"
        },
        {
          "character": "黑熊、贾信、马明、郭保、刘胜",
          "line_type": "同唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不亚如秦叔宝正气凛然。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黑熊",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众位弟兄，黄三哥今往衙中而去，你我大家赶到那里也得明白。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黑熊",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "计兄，你在此等候，我等去也。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黑熊",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "忙忙的寻知交方显情重，"
        },
        {
          "character": "黑熊",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "才能够就便里探知吉凶。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（黑熊、贾信、马明、郭保、刘胜同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "计全",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众英雄重义气令人钦敬，"
        }
      ],
